description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;University College London Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust (UCLH) where outstanding care and clinical excellence come together every day.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please note- you must be able to work day shifts between Monday - Friday for this role and have a minimum of 6 months NHS acute experience within the last 12 months to apply for this role.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;UCLH are looking for Nursing Assistants to join one of the largest and most successful Foundation Trusts in the UK.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why join UCLH?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Bank Nursing Assistants are invaluable to us and in return for their dedication and commitment, we offer the following benefits:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to work across all UCLH departments gaining invaluable skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to “Lines of Work” (short, medium or long term shifts)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Join our Pool of Nursing Assistants who are guaranteed shifts working at UCLH or the National Hospital for Neurology &amp; Neurosurgery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self service electronic timesheet submission, with weekly pay “No more paper timesheets”&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A designated onsite co-ordinator to offer support and introduce you to various departments within UCLH&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated recruitment team to ensure you can work as quickly as possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A bookings team to ensure you work when and wherever you want to&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return, we are looking for Nursing Assistants that can offer us:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for delivering excellent patient care and a minimum of 6 months recent experience in the NHS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are able to commit to working regular Long Day shifts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A willingness to learn new skills as we can offer training in some departments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to communicate effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to working well within a patient focused team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 6 Months in the NHS within the last 12 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you fit the above criteria, please apply today.&lt;/p&gt;
